civilians are getting caught in

19:08.047 --> 19:12.051 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
the middle. A warning: Some of
the images in this report may be

19:12.084 --> 19:17.156 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
disturbing. NICK SCHIFRIN: On
the outskirts of Maiduguri, the

19:17.189 --> 19:21.594 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
