for in divinely inspired

19:35.041 --> 19:37.009 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
confidence. There's a couple of
shotguns. There's a few

19:37.043 --> 19:39.011 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
machetes, a few knives, but
that's it. ABBA AJI KALLI,

19:39.045 --> 19:41.013 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
Civilian JTF: Yes. NICK
SCHIFRIN: I mean, what would you

19:41.047 --> 19:43.182 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
