ran into Boko Haram out here?

19:43.215 --> 19:45.184 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
MAN: We chased them out of
Maiduguri with stick and we

19:45.217 --> 19:50.990 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
