NICK SCHIFRIN:
Fifty-one-year-old Abba Aji

20:00.566 --> 20:03.936 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Kalli leads the civil JTF, for
Joint Task Force. He used to be

20:03.969 --> 20:06.472 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
