this way, where would we end up?

20:09.942 --> 20:11.911 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
ABBA AJI KALLI: If we kept
walking, we would end up in

20:11.944 --> 20:13.913 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Sambisa. NICK SCHIFRIN: In
Sambisa forest, their

20:13.946 --> 20:16.282 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
headquarters? ABBA AJI KALLI: In
the forest is the Boko Haram

20:16.315 --> 20:18.284 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
headquarters. NICK SCHIFRIN:
Down this road? ABBA AJI KALLI:

20:18.317 --> 20:20.286 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Down this road. NICK SCHIFRIN:
His men called call him elder.

